Title: Girl Vs. Monster
Genre: Action, Adventure, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Sci-Fi
Writer: Annie DeYoung (story), Annie DeYoung (teleplay), Ron McGee (teleplay)
Actors: Olivia Holt, Kerris Dorsey, Brendan Meyer, Katherine McNamara
Plot: A teen girl goes on a mission to recapture a dangerous monster that she accidentally released before it can do harm to her parents.
